(39, 137, 'Suchen', 'suchen', '', '<p>Die Komponente ‚ÄûSuchen‚Äú (‚Äûcom_search‚Äú) bietet eine grundlegende Suchfunktion f√ºr die Inhalte innerhalb der Komponenten einer Website. Viele Erweiterungen von Drittanbietern k√∂nnen mit diese Komponente ebenfalls durchsucht werden. <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Components_Search">Hilfe(engl.)</a></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 21, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-01-10 04:19:31', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":""}', 2, 0, 3, '', '', 1, 1, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, 'de-DE', ''),
